data.description: Nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac, this stunning home offers the epitome of luxury living. Boasting a paver driveway and a 3-car tandem garage, there's ample space for parking and storage. Step inside and you will be captivated by the open floor plan and elegant design. The interior is a perfect blend of style and functionality, featuring an owner's suite on both floors. Whether you're looking for a private retreat on the ground floor or a spacious escape upstairs, this home caters to your every need. Each suite boasts its own luxurious ensuite bathroom, providing the ultimate comfort and convenience. Cooking enthusiasts will fall in love with the large kitchen, equipped with 42” espresso wood cabinetry, sleek quartz countertops, slate appliances, and a generous butler's pantry. Preparing meals will be a delight in this well-appointed space. The adjacent breakfast area and family room are flooded with natural light, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. Heading upstairs, you'll find a versatile loft area, perfect for a home office, entertainment center, or cozy reading nook. The laundry room on this level ensures effortless chores, while plush carpets and ample closets in the additional bedrooms provide comfortable and organized living spaces. For those who love outdoor living, the back porch offers a fantastic spot for relaxing and entertaining. Overlooking the tranquil conservation area, imagine enjoying your morning coffee or hosting gatherings with friends and family in this idyllic outdoor space. The expansive green space surrounding the property provides plenty of room for outdoor parties, barbecues, or simply enjoying the Florida sunshine. This home not only offers outstanding features, but it is also part of a vibrant community with an array of amenities. Residents have access to the renowned Oasis Clubhouse at ChampionsGate, boasting a resort-style pool, spa, tennis, basketball courts, and an impressive golf course. The fitness center provides an opportunity for an active lifestyle, while an on-site concierge ensures convenience and ease. The Oasis Clubhouse takes entertainment to a whole new level, with a lazy river, water slides, beach entry, splash pad, putt-putt golf, fitness center, games room, tiki bar, and cabanas. It's like living in a perpetual vacation paradise right at your doorstep! This is a dream home that checks all the boxes, and it truly offers the best of Florida living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own!
